OL,5, Locals in tourist areas could be       
OL,6, alerted early on homes sold in their   
OL,7, area amid concerns some people are     
OL,8, being priced out of their communities. 
OL,10,FThe "fair chance scheme" will allow    
OL,11,Fproperties to be marketed locally only 
OL,12,Ffor a fixed period.                    
OL,14,FThe measure is part of a plan to       
OL,15,Fprotect Welsh as a community language, 
OL,16,Fthe Welsh government said.             
OL,18,F"For the Welsh language to thrive, we  
OL,19,Fneed sustainable communities," Welsh   
OL,20,FLanguage Minister Jeremy Miles said.   
